svg.title: Clouds of the genera Altocumulus, Altostratus and Nimbostratus: Altostratus translucidus
svg.desc: WMO international weather symbol: Clouds of the genera Altocumulus, Altostratus and Nimbostratus: Altostratus, the greater part of which is semitransparent; through this part the sun or moon may be weakly visible, as through ground glass
